metheus/main.go` lines 401-403) and validated via `toolkit_web.Validate()` (line 1145 in `main.go`).\n\nThe web configuration file allows enabling TLS and basic authentication for the entire web UI, complementing the admin API access control for more granular per-endpoint authorization."
}

